{"tid":1799691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會派聖誕禮物比手足...利物浦嗰英超冠軍仲有1.06","createTime":"2019-12-27T06:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T08:06:45.000Z","uid":60916,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"08a20160adc092165de983f46aa29118e22bee74","tid":1799691,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:52:39.000Z","msg":"聯賽踢左18場<br />\n利物浦累積左52分<br />\n領先主要對手曼城就14分<br />\n我就諗唔到曼城點追<br />\n就算利物浦剩底嗰20場出哂副選青年軍<br />\n都好難輸多過5場或者和多過8場<br />\n曼城依家就38分<br />\n就算贏哂剩底20場都係得98分<br />\n上季利物浦就97分<br />\n仲要今年利物浦踢得仲好過上年<br />\n多過97分係基本<br />\n點計都好<br />\n利物浦點都係head住曼<br />\n基本上穩攞英超架啦<br />\n馬會呢排搵夠係時候比手足賺下錢<br />\n1.06利物浦英超冠軍派下錢益手足<br />\n<br />\n出邊銀行年利率就3%(5個月你就當1.5%啦)<br />\n依家買利物浦冠軍5個月就賺6%<br />\n你每借100蚊就賺4.5蚊<br />\n陣間再借多幾億去買利物浦冠軍<br />\n咁就執多層樓<br />\n做人做狗自己決定<br />\n買利物浦英超冠軍<br />\n0風險6%回報"},{"pid":"f9cfb1b22c673d3c43ecaba219625d81e16737b7","tid":1799691,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"認真，真係送錢，但冇咁多錢買"},{"pid":"eb21e7485c72d4f30dfa8cd6c1a48b4db1515376","tid":1799691,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"我按左層樓 場場買利win滾上去"},{"pid":"7f7143e1c5aaa217ab79460b0dc43905a827d225","tid":1799691,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7737409dad7c7afe2bb7261281230884e036c33","tid":1799691,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"個個月出糧都買哂落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a283a44eed4677fe6e2e826e09372c57b7f33c6b","tid":1799691,"uid":209507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"開季就買晒成副身家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b55